title: I reset my Google pixel 3 I don't know my original account name and password
content: I reset my phone pixel 3 factory reset I don't know my new account name email or password ,phone is asking for original account synced with the phone. my other accounts that were synced with phone are working but won't unlock phone even though they backdate the resetting of the phone how do I resolve this issue, i I have used many emails and different numbers but I'm still the only sole owner of this device
